name: adsense_accounts_savedadstyles_list
description: List all saved ad styles in the specified account.

accountId.description: Account for which to list saved ad styles.

maxResults.description: The maximum number of saved ad styles to include in the response, used for paging.

pageToken.description: A continuation token, used to page through saved ad styles. To retrieve the next page, set this parameter to the value of "nextPageToken" from the previous response.

fields.description: Selector specifying which fields to include in a partial response.

key.description: API key. Your API key identifies your project and provides you with API access, quota, and reports. Required unless you provide an OAuth 2.0 token.

oauth_token.description: OAuth 2.0 token for the current user.

prettyPrint.description: Returns response with indentations and line breaks.

quotaUser.description: An opaque string that represents a user for quota purposes. Must not exceed 40 characters.

$ul: **etag**: ETag of this response for caching purposes.
**items**: The saved ad styles returned in this list response.
**kind**: Kind of list this is, in this case adsense#savedAdStyles. (default: adsense#savedAdStyles)
**nextPageToken**: Continuation token used to page through ad units. To retrieve the next page of results, set the next request's "pageToken" value to this.
